00:15:04.799 --> 00:15:08.760
If you don't have one of these at your org, a minimal package to package up your design

00:15:08.760 --> 00:15:11.799
system is super helpful.

00:15:11.799 --> 00:15:15.559
So you can put all your organization's colors into an easy-to-access list.

00:15:15.559 --> 00:15:19.599
This is going to save you all that time looking up hexes and remembering hexes.

00:15:19.599 --> 00:15:20.880
Amazing.

00:15:20.880 --> 00:15:24.479
And then just a minimal ggplot that gets you most of the way.

00:15:24.479 --> 00:15:27.799
If you have one of these at your org, people will love you.

00:15:27.799 --> 00:15:31.640
I maintain the one at my org now, and people love me just for that, and I didn't even create

